:"2021-05-24T18:08:20+00:00","updatedAt":"2021-05-24T18:08:20+00:00","version":1}}]},{"id":"26e8a6d9-0081-4823-9116-a7b8040df4cb","type":"manga","attributes":{"title":{"zh-ro":"Li\u00e8sh\u0101 W\u00fa \u00c0i"},"altTitles":[{"zh":"\u730e\u6740\u543e\u7231"},{"zh-ro":"Liesha Wu Ai"},{"en":"Kill My Love"},{"ko":"\ud0ac\ub9c1 \ub9c8\uc774 \ub7ec\ube0c"},{"en":"Killing My Love"}],"description":{"en":"Certain lovers are selected anonymously, only to find a strange symbol etched to their necks. Once those who are selected get too close to each other, or within the \u201cDanger Zone,\u201d one of them will die an explosive death. Suspicion, scheming, and murder\u2026 Once star crossed lovers, now enemies, willing to kill each other without hesitation\u2026   \nNing Yuan, a young emotionless man, is suddenly thrust into this cruel game of death. How will he protect his \u201cSoulmate?\u201d\n\n---\nLovers have been dying in the cruelest way possible. Victims were sliced up into pieces, as if their bodies had exploded. Andrea and Ian were mere bystanders to this spectacle until a misunderstanding throws them into \u201cKilling My Love\u201d (KML)!\n\nThis is a game that uses love to fuel murder. Each team of pairs are given targets that they must kill\u2026 or else. All the while, a sadistic gamemaster watches from the shadows.\n\nKML is a game with no end in sight, but one thing\u2019s for sure\u2026 this hell is just getting started.\n\n---\n**Official Translations:**\n* English: [INKR](https:\/\/inkr.com\/title\/1404-killing-my-love), [Tapas](https:\/\/tapas.io\/series\/killing-my-love\/info)\n* [Korean \/ \ud55c\uad6d\uc5b4](https:\/\/page.kakao.com\/home?seriesId=59485481)","it":"Alcuni amanti vengono selezionati in modo anonimo, solo per trovare uno strano simbolo inciso sul loro collo. Una volta che i selezionati si avvicinano troppo l'uno all'altro, o all'interno della \"Zona Pericolo\", uno di loro morir\u00e0 di una morte esplosiva. Sospetti, intrighi e omicidi... Un tempo amanti a stelle e strisce, ora nemici, disposti a uccidersi a vicenda senza esitazione... Ning Yuan, un giovane uomo senza emozioni, viene improvvisamente coinvolto in questo crudele gioco di morte. Come far\u00e0 a proteggere la sua \"Anima gemella\"?\n\n---\n**Official Translations:**\n* English: [INKR](https:\/\/inkr.com\/title\/1404-killing-my-love), [Tapas](https:\/\/tapas.io\/series\/killing-my-love\/info)\n* [Korean \/ \ud55c\uad6d\uc5b4](https:\/\/page.kakao.com\/home?seriesId=59485481)","zh":"\u533f\u540d\u63a8\u4e3e\u51fa\u6765\u7684\u604b\u4eba\u4eec\uff0c\u8116\u9888\u4e0a\u7a81\u7136\u6d6e\u73b0\u51fa\u4e00\u4e2a\u8be1\u5f02\u7684\u70b8\u5f39\u7b26\u53f7\uff0c\u5f7c\u6b64\u95f4\u4e00\u65e6\u8d8a\u8fc7\u4e86\u7279\u5b9a\u7684\u201c\u5371\u9669\u8ddd\u79bb\u201d\uff0c\u5c31\u4f1a\u8ba9\u5176\u4e2d\u4e00\u65b9\u7269\u7406\u6027\u7206\u70b8\u3002\u731c\u5fcc\u3001\u7b97\u8ba1\u3001\u8c0b\u6740\u2026\u2026\u76f8\u7231\u7684\u4eba\u4eec\u53cd\u76ee\u6210\u4ec7\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u62d4\u5200\u76f8\u5411\u2026\u2026\u5f53\u5929\u751f\u60c5\u611f\u7f3a\u5931\u7684\u9752\u5e74\u5b81\u8fdc\u88ab\u5377\u5165\u5230\u8fd9\u573a\u89c4\u5219\u6b8b\u5fcd\u7684\u6e38\u620f\uff0c\u53c8\u8981\u5982\u4f55\u4fdd\u62a4\u201c\u631a\u7231\u4e4b\u4eba\u201d\uff1f\n\n---\n**Official Translations:**\n* English: [INKR](https:\/\/inkr.com\/title\/1404-killing-my-love), [Tapas](https:\/\/tapas.io\/series\/killing-my-love\/info)\n* [Korean \/ \ud55c\uad6d\uc5b4](https:\/\/page.kakao.com\/home?seriesId=59485481)","es-la":"Los amantes han estado muriendo de la manera m\u00e1s cruel posible. Las v\u00edctimas fueron cortadas en pedazos, como si sus cuerpos hubieran explotado. \u00a1Andrea e Ian eran meros espectadores de este espect\u00e1culo hasta que un malentendido los arroja a \u201cKilling My Love\u201d (KML)!\n\nEste es un juego que usa el amor para alimentar el asesinato. A cada equipo de parejas se le asignan objetivos que deben matar... o de lo contrario. Mientras tanto, un maestro de juego s\u00e1dico observa desde las sombras.\n\nKML es un juego sin fin a la vista, pero una cosa es segura... este infierno reci\u00e9n comienza."},"isLocked":false,"links":{"al":"143905","ap":"killing-my-love","mu":"m7vatlk","raw":"https:\/\/www.kuaikanmanhua.com\/web\/topic\/9261\/","engtl":"https:\/\/comics.inkr.com\/title\/1404-killing-my-love?utm_source=mgd"},"officialLinks":null,"originalLanguage":"zh","lastVolume":"","lastChapter":"121","publicationDemographic":null,"status":"completed","year":2021,"contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"391b0423-d847-456f-aff0-8b0cfc03066b","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Action"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Romance"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Drama"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"cdc58593-87dd-415e-bbc0-2ec27bf404cc","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Fantasy"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"e197df38-d0e7-43b5-9b09-2842d0c326dd","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Web Comic"},"description":{},"group":"format","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"eabc5b4c-6aff-42f3-b657-3e90cbd00b75","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Supernatural"},"description":{},"group":"theme","version":1},"relationships":[]},{"id":"ee968100-4191-4968-93d3-f82d72be7e46","type":"tag","attributes":{"name":{"en":"Mystery"},"description":{},"group":"genre","version":1},"relationships":[]}],"state":"published","chapterNumbersResetOnNewVolume":false,"createdAt":"2021-03-03T07:12:55+00:00","updatedAt":"2025-12-26T23:29:21+00:00","version":11,"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","it","pl"],"latestUploadedChapter":"f6167487-5f4f-4184-afce-5e825591133a"},"relationships":[{"id":"9db4c458-2bcf-4865-a9bf-ec7aff2c824b","type":"author","attributes":{"name":"Xingkong She","imageUrl":null,"biography":{"en":"**Associated Names:**\n* \u661f\u7a7a\u793e\n* Antex\n* Comic Star Club\n* PIXTAR\n* Pxtar\n* Pxtar Manga Studio\n* Star Club\n* Yisehani\/Pxtar Manga Studio\n* \u7d20\u591c"},"twitter":null,"pixiv":null,"melonBook":null,"fanBox":null,"booth":null,"namicomi":null,"nicoVideo":null,"skeb":null,"fantia":null,"tumblr":null,"youtube":null,"weibo":"https:\/\/www.weibo.com\/pxtar","naver":null,"website":null,"createdAt":"2021-04-19T21:59:45+00:00","updatedAt":"2022-08-22T01:54:42+00:00","version":3}},{"id":"9db4c458-2bcf-4865-a9bf-ec7aff2c824b","type":"artist"},{"id":"38cce13b-7845-4fc2-a664-ae80f53ce53c","type":"cover_art","attributes":{"description":"","volume":null,"fileName":"1c4840ee-1a4c-4052-9dc1-58cd8a7d2b0d.jpg","locale":"zh","createdAt":"2021-05-24T18:33:36+00:00","updatedAt":"2023-05-31T00:49:13+00:00","version":3}}]},{"id":"82e71622-a17c-4673-a739-cc710d1a3cd4","type":"manga","attributes":{"title":{"en":"Sagikekkon Renaichuu"},"altTitles":[{"en":"Love in a Marriage of Lies"},{"ja":"\u8a50\u6b3a\u7d50\u5a5a\u30fb\u604b\u611b\u4e2d"}],"description":{"en":"Batoto Scans :  \n\u201cYou\u2019re so wet even though it\u2019s morning. If you don\u2019t wake up, I\u2019ll attack you ok?\u201d  \n  \n\u201cOh no!\u201d  \n  \nKomaki and Tasuku are newlyweds spending their time being lovey-dovey. Whether it's day or night, they can\u2019t help but want each other.  \n  \nBut there\u2019s a secret Tasuku can\u2019t tell Komaki. He used to be a host!!! In order to maintain his innocent image, he tries not to use the techniques he got from being a host, pretending to be a virgin.  \n  \nOn the other hand, Komaki also has a secret. She used to be Tasuku\u2019s stalker! Can she keep this a secret from her husband, the man she\u2019s always loved?  \n  \nThis is the love of 2 people trying to hide their past."},"isLocked":false,"links":{"al":"140884","ap":"sagikekkon-r